AI hallucinations

Case 1: Medical hallucination  
Research has shown that AI systems can generate incorrect medical information. In one study, AI was given fake medical terms and still produced confident explanations as if they were real. In some cases, AI accepted false medical information nearly half of the time.  
This demonstrates that AI can hallucinate in high-risk areas like healthcare, which may lead to dangerous consequences if users rely on the information without verification.
